### OpenCryptos Java Library ###

The first truly free, libre, and open source lightweight multiple cryptocurrencies java library (Bitcoin, Litecoin, Ethereum, etc) https://github.com/mrmx/opencryptos-java

    - Apache License Version 2.0

Forked from openwallet-android https://github.com/openwalletGH/openwallet-android
Uses Bitcoinj library https://bitcoinj.github.io